MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Mapping to load data from EXTERNAL_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER table into the EXTERNAL_CPS_NET_DEMAND table

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select customer_cd, demand_type, selling_style_cd, selling_color_cd, selling_attribute_cd, selling_size_cd, plant, demand_weekend_date, sum(current_qty) from EXTERNAL_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER where customer_cd=$$CUSTOMER_CD and selling_style_cd <> ' ' and selling_color_cd <> ' ' and selling_attribute_cd <> ' ' and selling_size_cd <> ' ' and revision_no <> -1 and plant is NOT NULL and demand_weekend_date is NOT NULL and current_qty > 0 group by customer_cd, demand_type, selling_style_cd, selling_color_cd, selling_attribute_cd, selling_size_cd, plant, demand_weekend_date order by customer_cd, demand_type, selling_style_cd, selling_color_cd, selling_attribute_cd, selling_size_cd, plant, demand_weekend_date
